criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. be hypertensive;

          2. age between 45 and 59 years old;

          3. not perform regular exercise;

          4. not use of beta-blockers drugs and calcium channel blockers;

          5. not be affected by labyrinthitis

          6. women be not in menopause;

          7. be not practitioners of VGA.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. modifying the antihypertensive treatment during treatment;

          2. Not have developed the ability to play during the adaptation period.
